PF2E System for foundryVTT
--------------------------
This template includes no PF2e system code, though cloning the system repo for
reference is well worth it. The PF2e system is licensed under Apache 2.0 — if
you copy any of its code into your module, comply with those terms. See
https://github.com/foundryvtt/pf2e/blob/v14-dev/LICENSE


